<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 prose prose-purple lg:prose-lg">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
    My First Elixir Phoenix Dating App
  </h1>

  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
    I recently embarked on a journey to build a dating app, and I chose Elixir and Phoenix as my tools. It was an exciting and challenging experience, and I learned a lot along the way.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">
    Why Elixir and Phoenix?
  </h2>

  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    I was drawn to Elixir and Phoenix for several reasons:
  </p>

  <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 list-disc pl-6">
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Concurrency:</span>
      Elixir, built on the Erlang VM, excels at handling concurrent requests, making it ideal for real-time applications like chat.
    </li>
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Productivity:</span>
      Phoenix provides a robust framework with features like LiveView, which enables real-time updates on the client without full page reloads, significantly enhancing the user experience.
    </li>
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Scalability:</span>
      Phoenix applications can easily scale horizontally to handle increasing traffic demands.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">
    Building the App
  </h2>

  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    Building the dating app involved several key aspects:
  </p>

  <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 list-disc pl-6">
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">User Authentication:</span>
      I implemented secure user registration, login, and password management.
    </li>
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Matching Algorithm:</span>
      I developed a basic matching algorithm to suggest potential matches based on user preferences.
    </li>
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Chat Functionality:</span>
      This was a challenging but rewarding part. I utilized Phoenix's PubSub system to implement real-time chat features, enabling users to communicate seamlessly.
    </li>
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Presence:</span>
      I implemented a presence system to track which users are currently online, enhancing the real-time experience.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">
    Hosting on Fly.io
  </h2>

  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
    Deploying the app to Fly.io was a smooth and enjoyable experience. Fly.io offers a developer-friendly platform with excellent performance and scalability. I was particularly impressed by how easily I could deploy and scale my application.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">
    Key Learnings
  </h2>

  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    This project taught me a lot about:
  </p>

  <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 list-disc pl-6">
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Elixir and Phoenix:</span>
      I gained a deeper understanding of these technologies and their capabilities.
    </li>
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Real-time applications:</span>
      I learned about the importance of presence, PubSub, and how to build responsive and engaging real-time experiences.
    </li>
    <li class="text-gray-700">
      <span class="font-semibold">Cloud deployment:</span>
      I gained valuable experience deploying and managing applications on a cloud platform.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">
    Conclusion
  </h2>

  <p class="text-gray-700">
    Building this dating app with Elixir and Phoenix was a fantastic learning experience. I am incredibly impressed with the performance and scalability of these technologies. While I encountered some challenges along the way, the overall experience was incredibly rewarding. I believe Elixir and Phoenix are an excellent choice for building real-time, scalable, and high-performance applications.
  </p>
</article>
